summary: Just a small dungeon mod that will maybe be expanded on with new weapons, enemies, areas and lore(?). So far it adds a weapon.
descriptionHtml:
Trials of Xarxes will maybe receive updates to lore and entities that were long forgotten to all but the Daedric prince of Secret Knowledge (or whatever I make up). So far adds a new weapon and a new enchantment(which is really op so unenchantble).

Location is below Throat of the world, on the path after High Hrothgar.
author: Samario
